    {
      "locale": "esES",
      "text": "«¿Conque esas tenemos? Entonces exijo satisfacción mediante un duelo, aquí y ahora».",
      "modification_date": "2026-06-01T08:46:49.0936795Z",
      "translated_from": "enGB",
      "translation_date": "2026-06-01T08:46:49.0936796Z",
      "original_text": "\"Is that so? Then I demand a duel, here and now.\"",
      "traits": [
        {
          "trait": "Translated",
          "trait_date": "2026-06-01T08:46:49.0936804Z",
          "locale_text": "«¿Conque esas tenemos? Entonces exijo satisfacción mediante un duelo, aquí y ahora»."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "locale": "zhCN",
      "text": "“是吗？那我要求决斗，就在此时，此地。”",
      "modification_date": "2026-06-01T08:49:02.0780865Z",
      "translated_from": "enGB",
      "translation_date": "2026-06-01T08:49:02.0780867Z",
      "original_text": "\"Is that so? Then I demand a duel, here and now.\"",
      "traits": [
        {
          "trait": "Translated",
          "trait_date": "2026-06-01T08:49:02.0780875Z",
          "locale_text": "“是吗？那我要求决斗，就在此时，此地。”"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "locale": "frFR",
      "text": "« Vraiment ? Dans ce cas, je vous défie en duel, ici et maintenant. »",
      "modification_date": "2026-06-02T08:53:11.9421986Z",
      "translated_from": "enGB",
      "translation_date": "2026-06-02T08:53:11.9421989Z",
      "original_text": "\"Is that so? Then I demand a duel, here and now.\"",
      "traits": [
        {
          "trait": "Translated",
          "trait_date": "2026-06-02T08:53:11.9422000Z",
          "locale_text": "« Vraiment ? Dans ce cas, je vous défie en duel, ici et maintenant. »"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "locale": "trTR",
      "text": "\"Öyle mi? O zaman tam burada ve şimdi bir düello talep ediyorum.\"",
      "modification_date": "2026-06-04T07:29:55.8394497Z",
      "translated_from": "enGB",
      "translation_date": "2026-06-04T07:29:55.8394499Z",
      "original_text": "\"Is that so? Then I demand a duel, here and now.\"",
      "traits": [
        {
          "trait": "Translated",
          "trait_date": "2026-06-04T07:29:55.8394504Z",
          "locale_text": "\"Öyle mi? O zaman tam burada ve şimdi bir düello talep ediyorum.\""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "locale": "jaJP",
      "text": "「そうなのか。ならば、今、ここで決闘を申し込む。」",
      "modification_date": "2026-06-05T13:06:41.4550730Z",
